'''凱爾特地區'''（{{lang-en|Celtic nations}}）是位於[[北歐|北歐]]及[[西歐|西歐]]的一系列地區的並稱。這一地區在過去或現在仍然使用[[凱爾特語|凱爾特語]]，並在藝術、歷史、音樂、舞蹈、文學等文化領域擁有共通的獨特之處<ref name=kochnation>{{cite book | last = Koch | first = John | authorlink = | coauthors = |title = Celtic Culture : A Historical Encyclopedia | publisher = ABL-CIO | year = 2005 | location =| pages = xx, 300, 421, 495, 512, 583, 985 | url = http://books.google.com/?id=f899xH_quaMC&printsec=frontcover&q=celtic+nation | doi =  | isbn = 978-1-85109-440-0 | accessdate = 24 November 2011}}</ref>。凱爾特地區包括了6個地區，分別是[[布列塔尼|布列塔尼]]（''Breizh''）、[[康沃爾郡|康沃爾郡]]（''Kernow''）、[[愛爾蘭|愛爾蘭]]（''Éire''）、[[曼島|曼島]]（''Mannin''）、[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]]（''Alba''）、[[威爾士|威爾士]]（''Cymru''）<ref name=kochnation/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.celticleague.net/index.html |title=Celticleague.net |accessdate=2013-11-18 |archive-date=2009-10-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091008133822/http://www.celticleague.net/index.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。這些地區至今仍然使用[[凱爾特語族|凱爾特語族]]的語言，或至現代為止都曾使用凱爾特語系語言<ref>{{cite book|last= Koch|first= John T.|coauthors= |title= Celtic Culture: A Historical Encyclopedia|publisher= ABC-CLIO|year= 2006|month= |pages= 365|url= http://books.google.com.au/books?id=f899xH_quaMC&printsec=frontcover&dq=Celtic+Culture:+A+Historical+Encyclopedia&source=bl&ots=p_YAf9AxXK&sig=GoBU0DW1RAo3_2SQW3PFMICrA5A&hl=en&ei=0nAXTI6LCJKekQWM6KWcCw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CCcQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q&f=false|accessdate= 2 March 2011|archive-date= 2013-10-23|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131023160627/http://books.google.com.au/books?id=f899xH_quaMC&printsec=frontcover&dq=Celtic+Culture:+A+Historical+Encyclopedia&source=bl&ots=p_YAf9AxXK&sig=GoBU0DW1RAo3_2SQW3PFMICrA5A&hl=en&ei=0nAXTI6LCJKekQWM6KWcCw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CCcQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url= no}}</ref>。除此之外，[[西班牙|西班牙]]西北部（[[加利西亞|加利西亞]]、[[阿斯圖里亞斯|阿斯圖里亞斯]]、[[坎塔布里亞|坎塔布里亞]]），[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]（和加利西亞接壤山區的部分地區）有時也被認為屬於凱爾特地區<ref name=Galicia>{{cite book|last= Koch|first= John T.|coauthors= |title= Celtic Culture: A Historical Encyclopedia|publisher= ABC-CLIO|year= 2006|month= |pages= 365, 697, 788–791|url= http://books.google.com.au/books?id=f899xH_quaMC&printsec=frontcover&dq=Celtic+Culture:+A+Historical+Encyclopedia&source=bl&ots=p_YAf9AxXK&sig=GoBU0DW1RAo3_2SQW3PFMICrA5A&hl=en&ei=0nAXTI6LCJKekQWM6KWcCw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CCcQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q&f=false|accessdate= 2 March 2011|archive-date= 2013-10-23|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20131023160627/http://books.google.com.au/books?id=f899xH_quaMC&printsec=frontcover&dq=Celtic+Culture:+A+Historical+Encyclopedia&source=bl&ots=p_YAf9AxXK&sig=GoBU0DW1RAo3_2SQW3PFMICrA5A&hl=en&ei=0nAXTI6LCJKekQWM6KWcCw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=3&ved=0CCcQ6AEwAg#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name=alberro>{{cite journal|first=Manuel|last=Alberro|url=http://www4.uwm.edu/celtic/ekeltoi/volumes/vol6/6_20/alberro_6_20.html|title=Celtic Legacy in Galicia|journal=E-Keltoi: Journal of Interdisciplinary Celtic Studies|volume=6|pages=1005–1035|year=2005|author=|access-date=2013-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130601144123/http://www4.uwm.edu/celtic/ekeltoi/volumes/vol6/6_20/alberro_6_20.html|archive-date=2013-06-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Festival 1">{{cite web
